Stats:
    Level: 00 (Cantrip)
    Name: Acid Splash
    School: Conjuration
    Casting Time: 1 Action
    Concentration :No
    Ritual: No
    Prepared: Always
    Gained From: Sorcerer, Wizard
    Target/Area of Effect: 5 Foot Sphere
    Range: 60 Feet
    Duration: Instantaneous
    Components:
        Verbal: Yes
        Somatic: Yes
        Material: No
        V, S
    Saving Throw: Dex
        on Success:
            No Damage
        on Failure:
            Full Damage
    Damage:

[[[[1+(floor(@{selected|level}/6))]]d6]]

You hurl a bubble of acid.
Choose one creature within range, or choose two creatures within range that are within 5 feet of each other.
A target must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take 1d6 acid damage.
This spells damage increases by 1d6 when you reach 5th Level (2d6), 11th level (3d6) and 17th level (4d6).
